text: This is a list of episodes from the ninth and final season of Alice. ==Episodes== ==Broadcast history== Alice began the season airing Sunday nights at 9:30-10:00 pm (EST) on October 14, 1984,TV Listings for October 14, 1984 before it was moved to the 8:30-9:00 pm (EST) Tuesday night time slot on January 8, 1985, where it remained through February 5.TV Listings for January 8, 1985TV Listings for January 8, 1985 In airing a two-part episode story, it also aired the next evening, Wednesday February 6, before returning to its Tuesday night timeslot, where it remained for the remainder of the TV season.TV Listings for March 19, 1985 ==References== Category:1984 American television seasons Category:1985 American television seasons
